@startuml pim-class-diagram
' Diagrama UML de classes simplificado do módulo PIM (estado atual recuperado).
' Fonte: engenharia reversa do checkpoint 02 (Figura 1 do relatório).
' Objetivo: recuperar a arquitetura mínima do fluxo de cadastro de colaborador,
' não representar todo o OrangeHRM.

title Módulo PIM - Classes do estado atual (cadastro de colaborador)

class AbstractVueController <<framework>> {
  + setComponent()
}

class SaveEmployeeController <<controller>> {
  + getIdGeneratorService()
  + preRender(request)
}

class Component <<view>> {
  - name
  - type
  - value
  + addProp(prop)
}

class IDGeneratorService <<service>> {
  + getNextID()
  + incrementID()
}

class EmployeeService <<service>> {
  - employeeDao
  - dispatcher
  + saveEmployee(employee)
  + getEmployeeById(id)
}

class EmployeeDao <<dao>> {
  + getEmployeeListByParams()
  + saveEmployee(employee)
  + deleteEmployees(ids)
}

class QueryBuilderWrapper <<orm>> {
  + getQueryBuilder()
}

class Employee <<entity>> {
  - empNumber
  - empId
  - firstName
  - lastName
  - workEmail
  - eventDate
  + getters/setters
}

database "Banco de Dados\n(tabelas de domínio PIM)" as DB

SaveEmployeeController --|> AbstractVueController : herda
SaveEmployeeController --> Component : monta props
SaveEmployeeController --> IDGeneratorService : consulta
SaveEmployeeController --> EmployeeService : usa
EmployeeService --> EmployeeDao : consulta/persiste
EmployeeService --> Employee : manipula
EmployeeDao --> QueryBuilderWrapper : consulta
QueryBuilderWrapper --> DB : SQL/ORM
EmployeeDao ..> Employee : retorna

note bottom of Employee
  Classe central do domínio. Agrega salário, contrato,
  dependentes, contatos, documentos e qualificações.
  Code smell: Large Class / God Class.
end note

note bottom of EmployeeDao
  Concentra filtros, joins, paginação e critérios de busca.
  Code smell: Long Method / Complex Query.
end note

@enduml
